  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>M.E.M.O. at USC is a student-run nonprofit focused on serving underserved communities through medical and educational initiatives locally and in Vietnam.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="programs">
    <h2>Our Programs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Heart Program:</strong> Funds surgeries for children with heart defects.</li>
      <li><strong>Hope Program:</strong> Supports orphanages with health and education supplies.</li>
      <li><strong>Scholarship Program:</strong> Keeps students in school with donations.</li>
      <li><strong>Dental Program:</strong> Offers cleanings and dental care in underserved areas.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="missiontrip">
    <h2>Mission Trip</h2>
    <p>Each year, USC MEMO travels to Vietnam with doctors and students to set up mobile health clinics, deliver care, and distribute resources.</p>
  </section>

